              <strong> Active Reservations 
                <img src="/public/images/searchIcon.jpg" width="7%" style="cursor: pointer;" 
                onclick="toggleActiveReservationsSearchBar()" class="ml-1" alt="Search"> </strong> &nbsp; &downarrow;
